      <title>开始新的一天你需要知道的五件事：美洲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-10-07/five-things-you-need-to-know-to-start-your-day-americas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[早上好。美国 10 年期国债收益率回升至 4% 以上，交易员权衡经济乐观情绪与中东紧张局势，华尔街专家对股市的看法也愈发乐观。以下是市场走势。—  David Goodman]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-10-07/five-things-you-need-to-know-to-start-your-day-americas</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 10:30:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国券商跳过节假日，为“忙碌”复工招聘员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/china-s-brokers-skip-holidays-to-staff-up-for-hectic-reopening</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的券商和证券交易所正准备迎接周二的繁忙景象，因为在为期一周的假期后，国内股市将重新开市，而市场普遍乐观地认为，中国政府的刺激措施将再次推动股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/china-s-brokers-skip-holidays-to-staff-up-for-hectic-reopening</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 10:23:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Equinor 斥资 25 亿美元收购丹麦风电巨头 Orsted 的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/orsted-shares-jump-after-equinor-buys-stake-in-wind-giant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Equinor ASA 以 25 亿美元收购了丹麦风能巨头 Orsted A/S 的股份，将北欧地区最大的化石燃料公司之一与最大的可再生能源开发商整合在一起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/orsted-shares-jump-after-equinor-buys-stake-in-wind-giant</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 10:13:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃利奥特在英国败诉，因伦敦金属交易所关闭镍市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/elliott-loses-uk-appeal-over-lme-s-nickel-market-shutdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于伦敦金属交易所 (London Metal Exchange) 做出了有争议的决定，阻止镍市场失控的空头挤压，埃利奥特投资管理公司 (Elliott Investment Management) 在英国失去了吸引力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/elliott-loses-uk-appeal-over-lme-s-nickel-market-shutdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 09:44:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储重新考虑政策，美国主要债券收益率自 8 月以来首次触及 4%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/key-us-yields-near-4-for-first-time-since-august-on-fed-rethink</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于就业报告强劲，削弱了美联储再次大幅降息的可能性，主要美国国债收益率回升至 4%，为 8 月份以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/key-us-yields-near-4-for-first-time-since-august-on-fed-rethink</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 07:41:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国工厂订单下降是工业衰退的另一个迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/german-factory-orders-drop-in-yet-another-sign-of-industry-woe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国八月份工厂订单大幅下降，标志着欧洲最大经济体德国在今年未能实现期待已久的复苏，其工业再次遭遇挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/german-factory-orders-drop-in-yet-another-sign-of-industry-woe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 06:08:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马尔代夫重新转向印度以缓解中国债务压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/maldives-seeks-to-repair-ties-with-india-as-debt-crisis-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马尔代夫总统一年前上台，力图将印度排除在该国事务之外，与中国拉近关系。如今，随着债务危机的临近以及中国先前发放的贷款即将到期，他正在新德里寻求修复两国关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/maldives-seeks-to-repair-ties-with-india-as-debt-crisis-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 05:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
